In this edition of Inzeit Man starring Trendzel Washington, Jack and Miles discuss Premier League transfers, Waukesha, WI school district denying children lunches, Scott Zolak claiming rap music is 'hurting' Cam Newton, Judge John Cooper overturning DeSantis' executive order, Hurricane Ida hitting the Gulf Coast, and the new 'Candyman' reboot
